{"tid":1680754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民間記者會有野想我地幫手","createTime":"2019-10-29T04:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T05:51:03.000Z","uid":22556,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"cb1aba5a652eea7f823b7404ebfb6013f49bdb02","tid":1680754,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T04:05:19.000Z","msg":"民間記者會之<br />\n[10.28民間研究]<br />\n<br />\n問卷link: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.citizenspc.org/survey\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.citizenspc.org%2Fsurvey&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFP1DHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=d5788127\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.citizenspc.org/survey</a><br />\n<br />\n由六月至今，香港人經歷了大大小小一連串密集的社會運動，我們希望以今次問卷研究，了解抗爭者至今的心理健康、社交狀況，以及對整個運動的意見，為反送中運動作出系統性、科學化的數據收集及建議。是次問卷調查直至10月29日晚上8時59分截止，希望大家支持。<br />\n<br />\nWe would once again like to conduct a survey on 28th October, for the purpose of collecting empirical data on the mental health status, social functioning, as well as the public opinion on the Movement for quantitative analysis.<br />\n<br />\nThe deadline for submission is 8:59pm on Tuesday 29th October 2019."},{"pid":"6349e5896ba24f3555d7a4610448c71d9fd761e3","tid":1680754,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T04:07:30.000Z","msg":"$1交稅攬炒機械人小測成績表已出！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1679773\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1679773</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"924f8430fd3cdf399b45323e087f91d1a65d45d7","tid":1680754,"uid":243198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T04:17:24.000Z","msg":"又一奶共機構請777開會!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680169\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680169</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">緊急！林奠11.7會去灣仔！<br />\n幫手推呀！</span></span>"},{"pid":"391b71b97c4475408a4c285e301dd42d9a646f9e","tid":1680754,"uid":